== Grassroots Policy

GrassrootsPolicy.com is a website developed in Ruby on Rails, hosted on Heroku.  The idea of the site is that users post, vote, and comment on political ideas. If you feel passionate about an idea you can share the link with your friends, and encourage them to provide feedback and vote on the issue.  Top ideas might get the attention of elected officials who can do something about it.

== Rails Libraries

gem 'devise' - Used for user registration and sign-in.

gem 'awesome-nested-sets' - Used for comment threading.

jQuery / jQuery UI - Linked from Microsoft CDN.

jQuery Templates - used for rendering JSON as HTML.

